reviewText: Fast service - great product ... just as advertised.

A nice intro into The Rolling Stones. I wanted to know what separated them for others. As you begin to watch their story, it is amazing to view the personalities of the band members and how they grew and changed to become what they are today. I would recommend to anyone who loves the Stones and a good intro to those that never followed them before.
more information about "the Stones",and I have been listening to them ince 1964. I thoroughly enjoyed this DVD.
Pretty good look at the early influence of Brian Jones on the Stones evolution as great act.
